igh ds and defensive proc to be pretty insane dps.&lt;p&gt;Message Edited by Orruar on &lt;span class=date_text&gt;12-06-2005&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=time_text&gt;09:57 PM&lt;/span&gt;</description>
